[I] Shader translation library for SDL's GPU API.

[T] This is a library for translating shaders to different formats, intended
[T] for use with SDL's GPU API. It takes SPIRV or HLSL as the source and
[T] outputs DXBC, DXIL, SPIRV, MSL, or HLSL.

